TailwindCSS Styling

-Utility-First Design: Follow Tailwind’s utility classes for styling (flex, grid, p-4, bg-gray-100).

-Responsiveness: Implement sm:, md:, lg:, xl: breakpoints for mobile-first design.

-Animations: Use Tailwind’s built-in animation utilities (transition, animate-spin, hover:bg-opacity-75).

-Dark Mode Support: Utilize dark: classes for a seamless dark mode experience.

-Custom Themes: Extend Tailwind configuration using tailwind.config.js
